---
title: Roasted Cauliflower with Bulgur, Tzatziki, and Chili Cumin Oil
description: Think cauliflower is forever destined to be a side dish? Think again! Roasting the creamy white vegetable transforms it into the star of the meal. In this recipe, it’s nestled between a drizzle of yogurt and cucumber tzatziki and a bed of hearty bulgur.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/roasted-cauliflower-steaks-7ecb1b9f.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/roasted-cauliflower-steaks-d061e000.pdf
nutrition:
  calories: 463 kcal
  fat: 25 g
  saturated fat: 4 g
